lead_paragraph: Brandt Snedeker now has four PGA Tour victories in which he started at least five shots out of the lead in the final round. The Farmers Insurance Open followed the script of his previous comeback except for one big difference.

headline.print_headline: A Perfect Storm Works Out Perfectly for Snedeker
